msgstr "Sinov uchun kamida bitta matematik kutubxona tanlashingiz kerak"

#: src/mathlib.c:875
#, c-format
msgid ""
"This will run a frequency loop benchmark for each detected linear algebra "
"library and then provide a summary.  It may take some time to complete "
"depending on how big and how many frequencies your NEC2 will use. Detailed "
"timing will be provided in the terminal.\n"
"\n"
"Notes:\n"
"* Only one Intel MKL library can be tested without restarting xnec2c, so "
"select which one you wish to benchmark before proceeding or it will choose "
"the first in the list and skip the rest.\n"
"\n"
"* Thread congestion will occur for multi-threaded libraries when using the -"
"j N option if there are not enough CPUs available to accommodate the forked "
"processes in combination with library threads.  Consider reducing the value "
"of -j N for benchmarking to find what library works best with a mix of "
"forking and threading; you can use `top` to monitor your CPU usageand if it "
"reaches 0%% idle then you might consider reducing -j N.\n"
"\n"
"You may wish to experiment setting these environment variables:\n"
"  * OPENBLAS_NUM_THREADS=N\t# OpenBLAS thread limit\n"
"  * OMP_NUM_THREADS=N\t\t# OpenMP thread limit\n"
"  * MKL_NUM_THREADS=N\t\t# Intel MKL thread limit\n"
"\n"
"Click OK to proceed, this dialog will close when complete."
msgstr ""
"Bu har bir aniqlangan chiziqli algebra kutubxonasi uchun chastota aylanishi "
"sinovini bajaradi va keyin xulosani taqdim etadi. NEC2 qancha katta va "
"qancha chastotalardan foydalanishiga qarab bajarilishi biroz vaqt olishi "
"mumkin. Batafsil vaqtlash terminalde koʻrsatiladi.\n"
"\n"
"Eslatmalar:\n"
"* Faqat bitta Intel MKL kutubxonasi xnec2c ni qayta ishga tushirmasdan "
"sinovdan oʻtkazilishi mumkin, shuning uchun davom etishdan oldin qaysi "
"birini sinab koʻrishni tanlang, aks holda roʻyxatdagi birinchisini tanlaydi "
"va qolganlarini oʻtkazib yuboradi.\n"
"\n"
"* Koʻp oqimli kutubxonalar uchun -j N parametridan foydalanganda, "
"tarmoqlangan jarayonlarni kutubxona iplari bilan birgalikda qoʻllash uchun "
"yetarli protsessorlar mavjud boʻlmasa, ip toʻqnashuvi yuzaga keladi. Qaysi "
"kutubxona tarmoqlash va iplash aralashmasida eng yaxshi ishlashini topish "
"uchun sinovda -j N qiymatini kamaytiring; protsessor foydalanishini kuzatish "
"uchun `top` dan foydalaning va agar 0%% boʻsh vaqtga yetsa -j N ni "
"kamaytirishni oʻylab koʻring.\n"
"\n"
"Quyidagi muhit oʻzgaruvchilarini sozlab koʻrishingiz mumkin:\n"
"  * OPENBLAS_NUM_THREADS=N\t# OpenBLAS ip chegarasi\n"
"  * OMP_NUM_THREADS=N\t\t# OpenMP ip chegarasi\n"
"  * MKL_NUM_THREADS=N\t\t# Intel MKL ip chegarasi\n"
"\n"
"Davom etish uchun OK tugmasini bosing, ushbu muloqot oynasi tugagach "
"yopiladi."

